<br>
Actually, I talked to a friend yesterday in another guild, and if I can get out leaders to liaise (oh yes, blue collar lingo!), it could go places as both our guilds have around 30 members or so.  Even if the uniting guilds doesn't work, I'll try to work an alliance.<br>
